channel.title: Un-changeable values?
channel.description:
Well for some reason there are some values that no matter what i change them too, they effect in the game is the exact same.
For example, I've gone into player.java to change the login position for new members. I changed the values to the coordinates i wanted, compiled, ran the server and STILL when i log in as a new member its the old coordinates not the new. I've searched but can't find what i did wrong or what else i needed to change but nothing came up.
Also, It wont let me change one of the emote teleports
I've gone to the right case, and edited the coordinates but it still teleports me to the old coordinates, no matter what i change.
Any help here would be awesome
